Membership
Delray Dunes Golf & Country Club offers a wide range of social, dining, golf and fitness activities, all designed to accommodate your individual lifestyle.
Delray Dunes members enjoy an active calendar of events each season. Residency in the Delray Dunes community is not required for membership.
If you are considering moving to the Palm Beach area and are ready for the reward of a truly private, friendly, welcoming club, Delray Dunes is the perfect fit for you. Whether you are retired, a young professional, living on the ocean or intracoastal, or spend part of your year up north, Delray Dunes offers incomparable service in an elegant, private club atmosphere. Delray Dunes is a great place for active people who love to play golf and enjoy the country club lifestyle.
Membership for non-residents is by invitation only and requires a sponsoring member and a seconder. For more information about membership at Delray Dunes Golf & Country Club, please call our Membership Director at
(561) 732-1600
, or via e-mail at
[email protected]
. Membership is mandatory for homeowners at Delray Dunes.
